data.description: This stunning triplex has undergone a meticulous renovation, ensuring a contemporary living experience for its future residents.    Units A and B each feature two spacious bedrooms and one well-appointed bathroom, providing a cozy and inviting atmosphere. The thoughtful design of these units maximizes space and functionality, creating a comfortable retreat for occupants.    Unit 3 boasts three bedrooms and two bathrooms. With generous living spaces, this unit provides ample room for both relaxation and entertainment. The master suite includes a private bath, adding a touch of luxury to everyday living.    The renovations throughout the triplex showcase modern finishes, high-quality materials, and attention to detail. From upgraded kitchens with sleek appliances to stylish bathroom fixtures, every aspect has been carefully crafted to enhance the overall living experience.    Conveniently located and impeccably designed, this renovated triplex is the perfect place to call home. Don't miss the opportunity to be a part of this exceptional living experience. Contact us now to schedule a viewing and make this triplex your next home.  -    Unit c is occupied. The rest of the units are not.
